   <title outputclass="Heading 3" class="- topic/title ">
      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">7.103</ph> Agency-head responsibilities.</title>
   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <p id="fnJnDc" outputclass="Text Body" class="- topic/p ">(S-90) A written plan (combined AS/AP, standard, or
         streamlined) shall also be prepared for high risk contracts/CLINs as defined in subpart
         7.101 (See Table 7-1 for thresholds and approval authority).</p>
      <p id="KQauPY" outputclass="Ctr normal" class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Table 7-1 Acquisition Plan Thresholds and Approvals</b>
      </p>
